dct_title_s: Pas-caart van Zuyd-Zee, tusschen California en ilhas de Ladrones
dct_alternative_sm: La Atlas del mundo o el mundo aguado
dct_description_sm: ... Hendrick Doncker Boekverkooper en Graadboogh maker inde Nieubrughsteegh in’t Stuurmans Gereetshap.

Sea chart of the Pacific, with East at the top and the equator running down the middle. The northwestern tip of California is shown and labelled “I. CALIFORNIA”, and with 4 place names: C. Blanco, P.St.Francisco Draco, P.de Monte Rey, and P.de la Conception. Also included are partial outlines of: Compagnies Landt, Japan, Staten Lant, Ant van Diemens Lant.
Title cartouche with cherubs at top right.
Issued in his La Atlas del mundo o el mundo aguado. -- Amsterdam, [1669].
